/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[AddShow]    Script Date: 23-09-2020 15:44:26 ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[AddShow]
    @HallId int,
    @MovieId int,
    @Date date,
    @StartTime time,
	@EndTime time
AS

Declare @vCount int

Select @vCount = count(*) FROM Shows WHERE @Date = Date AND @HallId = HallId AND (EndTime > @StartTime AND StartTime < @EndTime)

if @vCount > 0
BEGIN
	select 0
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO Shows (HallId, MovieId, Date, StartTime, EndTime)
	VALUES (@HallId, @MovieId, @Date, @StartTime, @EndTime)
	select 1
END

GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GetMovies]
		@movieId int
AS
if @movieId != 0
BEGIN
SELECT [Id]
	  ,[Name]
      ,[Length]
      ,[Description]
      ,[Genre]
	  ,[IMG]
  FROM [BiografDatabase].[dbo].[Movie]
      where @movieId = Id
END
else
begin
SELECT [Id]
	  ,[Name]
      ,[Length]
      ,[Description]
      ,[Genre]
	  ,[IMG]
  FROM [BiografDatabase].[dbo].[Movie]

end
